summary: In both the first kiss (Vendredi 20h27) and the reunion kiss (Vendredi 18h35), Lucas launches himself at Elliot's face with...
body: In both the first kiss (Vendredi 20h27) and the reunion kiss (Vendredi 18h35), Lucas launches himself at Elliot’s face with sheer want, need and magnetism. He free falls into the kissed like he can’t breathe and Elliot is his air supply. Then Elliot just instinctively holds his face and kisses him like he’s afraid to ever let go, like he’s trying to protect them both by holding on. It’s too beautiful for my human heart to bear.
